description: Asarum europaeum [TA]. i. "Asarum europaeum Lin: Asara- bacca. Anglis. ex horto" [JL].

Linnaea borealis [JL]. i. Cites Linn. Sp. Pl. 631; Bauh. Pin. 93. ii. "This is a Native of Sweden, Sibiria, Switzerland, Russia, Canada, & c.
